{
  "texts": [
    "SFT is still enough.",
    "Another intriguing observation is that none of the alignment methods outperform SFT in MMLU (See Table 1).",
    "This suggests that SFT remains superior to other methods for multitask understanding.",
    "Additionally, apart from the KTO algorithm in reasoning, truthfulness, and question answering, SFT demonstrates comparable performance (See Reasoning, Question Answering, and Truthfulness plots in Figure 2).",
    "This indicates that alignment methods struggle to achieve notable performance improvements in these tasks."
  ]
